  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Multiple Locations) [EL]",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Respobsibilities:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate forklifts safely to move, load, and unload goods while following safety protocols.</li>\n  <li>Assist with receiving, sorting, and storing goods, ensuring inventory accuracy.</li>\n  <li>Pick, pack, and label items for delivery, ensuring timely and accurate dispatch.</li>\n  <li>Keep the warehouse clean and organized, and perform basic equipment checks.</li>\n  <li>Follow safety guidelines, participate in drills, and comply with company procedures.</li>\n  <li>Handle inventory tasks such as receiving, releasing, packing, and assembling items as needed.</li>\n  <li>Manage stock levels efficiently using inventory control methods.</li>\n  <li>Take on additional tasks like housekeeping, facility maintenance, and basic technical work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to handle the job's physical demands, including working extended periods under the sun.</li>\n  <li>Demonstrates a positive work attitude, self-motivation, and a strong sense of responsibility.</li>\n  <li>Proactive, with good organizational skills to coordinate and liaise effectively with customers, logistics partners, suppliers, and internal teams.</li>\n  <li>Willing to learn and flexible to work long hours when required (OT pay is provided).</li>\n  <li>Valid Class 3 license, if have forklift license will be good too.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
